      "message": "Patch Set 1: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/6e951c70-1c0f-11e3-9f8e-52540035b04c).  Ran 16 tests.  2 tests failed: conf-sanity, sanity.",
