      "date": "2013-09-13 18:31:26.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nI think with  http://review.whamcloud.com/7625, we do not need this patch any more, because mdt_object_find will return error for invalidate/stale FID lookup anyway. So any object after successful lookup should be either remote or exists. This LBUG should help us to catch other problem.",
